social_posts.post_text: This love at first sight, baby
Never have to do too much

I am currently crying… My precious baby girl. Mommy is not ready for this post!🥹

Happy 1st birthday to my Alaina Rose, my lai lai, my rosey girl, MY DAUGHTER !!!🥹🩷 You have shown mommy true love!!! I don’t think I truly started living until I had you. You are such a happy loving girl. You bring a smile to everyone you meet! You have such a personality already. Thank you God for sending me this beautiful soul. Baby girl you have made motherhood an easy and rewarding thing to take on. Mommy was ready for you!!😭 I’m always always always going to protect you and mommy will always be there. I love you and can’t wait for our future trips and our future life 🩷🩷🩷 you are my everything. I love you so much.
Pretty & fine like my girls i came with ❤️‍🔥
Christmas with my Lai Lai girl🫀🎄🥂❤️
